data.enText: a period of new life, growth or activity
the seasonal cycle of death and rebirth

data.chText: （信仰加强或皈依另一宗教后精神上的）新生，再生
data.enText: a spiritual change when a person's faith becomes stronger or they convert to another religion

simple_means.memory_skill: re 一再，重新 + birth 出生 → 再生，新生

means: (信仰加强或皈依另一宗教后精神上的)新生，再生

tr: a spiritual enlightenment causing a person to lead a new life
the revival of learning and culture
after death the soul begins a new cycle of existence in another human body

value.def: You can refer to a change that leads to a new period of growth and improvement in something as its rebirth .

example.ex: ...the rebirth of democracy in Latin America...
example.tran: 民主在拉丁美洲的复兴

example.ex: The hotel is awaiting its rebirth.
